As if they needed reminding

1055
01:28:25.096 --> 01:28:28.331
what would happen if her future
couldn't be secured.


1056
01:28:29.667 --> 01:28:31.969
Then with the nation's
pride at stake,


1057
01:28:32.637 --> 01:28:35.372
the British Government
stepped in
with a financial commitment,


1058
01:28:35.405 --> 01:28:36.874
to guarantee completion.

1059
01:28:38.308 --> 01:28:41.344
With Clydebank's
future at stake,


1060
01:28:42.113 --> 01:28:43.681
the workers stepped in.

1061
01:28:44.515 --> 01:28:46.517
To guarantee her success.

1062
01:28:47.685 --> 01:28:49.854
And that of future generations.

1063
01:28:52.290 --> 01:28:54.725
Crime locks many doors.

1064
01:28:57.995 --> 01:28:59.530
But for one prisoner,

