1085
01:30:17.375 --> 01:30:19.210
Yeah.

1086
01:30:19.243 --> 01:30:21.812
Well, it's not exactly
on the curriculum at university,


1087
01:30:21.846 --> 01:30:23.247
but yeah, sure.

1088
01:30:23.681 --> 01:30:25.950
From time-to-time cases
have occurred.


1089
01:30:26.150 --> 01:30:27.551
I mean, it's an open secret.

1090
01:30:27.652 --> 01:30:29.987
Even kids' rhymes are about it.

1091
01:30:30.087 --> 01:30:32.156
London Bridge keeps
falling down until...


1092
01:30:32.189 --> 01:30:34.792
