we're unsinkable?!


1096
01:30:45.236 --> 01:30:48.506
Might explain
how the ship
survived a World War


1097
01:30:49.106 --> 01:30:51.676
a dozen botched face lifts,

1098
01:30:52.143 --> 01:30:53.511
a rogue wave.

1099
