rTo reinstate the ship's power,
we must reinstate Mr Clark,


1100
01:31:01.619 --> 01:31:05.056
and kill whatever
flesh he is in.


1101
01:31:18.436 --> 01:31:19.904
Should we fail...

1102
01:31:21.339 --> 01:31:24.241
...your question as to whether
this ship is unsinkable...


1103
01:31:26.911 --> 01:31:29.647
