- Stay with us, please.


1129
01:35:29.621 --> 01:35:30.622
Lukas?

1130
01:35:30.655 --> 01:35:31.989
If you wish to stay,

1131
01:35:32.122 --> 01:35:34.091
y- y- you could take my place!

1132
01:35:34.124 --> 01:35:36.595
I really don't mind!

1133
01:35:36.961 --> 01:35:40.130
It's wonderful,
wonderful fun!


1134
01:35:40.431 --> 01:35:41.999
And I could leave...

1135
01:35:42.733 --> 01:35:44.735
just for
a little while.


1136
01:35:44.768 --> 01:35:46.470
You don't understand!

1137
01:35:46.504 --> 01:35:47.805
I've been here for so long!

1138
01:35:47.838 --> 01:35:49.507
I promise,
I'll come back.


1139
01:35:49.541 --> 01:35:51.175
