01:36:28.613 --> 01:36:29.714
Er...

1153
01:36:30.080 --> 01:36:32.249
yeah, we got lost
on the way out.


1154
01:36:36.755 --> 01:36:38.489
Have you seen Anne anywhere?

1155
01:36:39.223 --> 01:36:40.357
No.

1156
01:36:45.262 --> 01:36:46.330
Who's that?

1157
01:36:46.531 --> 01:36:48.032
That's nobody.

1158
01:36:51.168 --> 01:36:52.169
You sure?

1159
01:36:52.637 --> 01:36:53.837
Yeah.

1160
01:36:56.874 --> 01:36:58.475
So, so that...

1161
01:36:58.777 --> 01:37:00.578
that's not her on the trolley?

1162
01:37:01.412 --> 01:37:02.514
Oh, him?

1163
01:37:03.581 --> 01:37:05.449
No, it's just, er...

1164
01:37:07.151 --> 01:37:12.122
just some vagrant I caught,
er, sneaking around.


1165
01:37:16.695 --> 01:37:18.095
Okay.

1166
01:37:19.096 --> 01:37:20.364
Okay.

1167
01:37:20.397 --> 01:37:23.067
Er, we, we found the
swimming pool,
by the way.


1168
01:37:23.100 --> 01:37:25.737
You're right, she's,
she's a, she's a pearl.


1169
01:37:26.236 --> 01:37:29.674
And the, er, little brat
who absconded in your
son's place?


1170
01:37:29.708 --> 01:37:31.308
She told us everything.

1171
01:37:33.778 --> 01:37:35.879
Now, I was hoping you'd, er,
return with her,


1172
01:37:35.913 --> 01:37:39.517
