1174
01:37:44.054 --> 01:37:46.023
If we don't walk out
of here tomorrow,
call the cops.


1175
01:37:46.056 --> 01:37:48.292
Tell them everything. Okay?

1176
01:37:48.459 --> 01:37:53.864
So even if that was true,
who'd believe her stories?


1177
01:37:53.931 --> 01:37:59.002
Well, actually,
a lot of people would.


1178
01:37:59.870 --> 01:38:02.674
Whatever secrets you've kept
hidden down here,


1179
01:38:02.707 --> 01:38:04.108
Lukas saw.

1180
01:38:04.375 --> 01:38:05.643
Okay, he saw them.

1181
01:38:07.878 --> 01:38:09.213
Give that to me.

1182
01:38:09.279 --> 01:38:10.615
No. No, no, no.

1183
01:38:10.815 --> 01:38:14.184
Not until we're safely
off the ship.


1184
01:38:25.262 --> 01:38:28.198
Move, move, move!
Where's that boy?


1185
01:38:31.803 --> 01:38:33.303
Clarky!

1186
01:38:42.312 --> 01:38:45.315
As we approach
the next stop of our tour,


1187
01:38:45.382 --> 01:38:47.619
we are reminded in these
hallowed halls


1188
01:38:47.652 --> 01:38:51.088
of how insignificant
we really are.


1189
01:38:51.121 --> 01:38:53.892
When even a ship as hardy
as the Queen Mary


1190
01:38:53.924 --> 01:38:55.926
could be brought to her knees.

1191
01:38:56.226 --> 01:39:00.164
The year 1942,
she was en route to Scotland


1192
01:39:00.197 --> 01:39:03.535
with ten thousand, three hundred
and ninety-eight soldiers,


1193
01:39:03.568 --> 01:39:06.538
and nine hundred and fifty
crew on board.


1194
01:39:06.704 --> 01:39:11.008
Duly recorded on the ship's log
is the date and time,


1195
01:39:11.175 --> 01:39:14.646
the course, the destination,
weather conditions,


1196
01:39:15.012 --> 01:39:16.514
temperature,

1197
01:39:16.548 --> 01:39:18.550
longitude and latitude.

1198
01:39:18.683 --> 01:39:23.420
But what is never recorded
is the fear that washes
over a deck


1199
01:39:23.588 --> 01:39:25.389
like fog and ocean spray,

1200
01:39:25.422 --> 01:39:28.492
as a ninety foot rogue
wave appears.


1201
01:39:28.560 --> 01:39:32.329
Yes, the RMS Queen Mary
is a frightened ship,


1202
01:39:32.362 --> 01:39:37.167
