1208
01:41:02.052 --> 01:41:03.220
Anne, please come in.

1209
01:41:03.253 --> 01:41:04.722
Fuck.

1210
01:41:10.795 --> 01:41:12.195
Oh.

1211
01:41:19.504 --> 01:41:20.538
Lukas?

1212
